<p>KidMix takes no responsibility for the actions or events that occur before, during, or after a scheduled playdate. We advise that parents communicate with each other to finalize actual playdate activities. We are not responsible for any activities that occur during a physical playdate. We are only a scheduling system to help facilitate the coordination of a playdate between children.</p>

<h4>SmartZone</h4>

<p>The KidMix Application includes the KidMix SmartZone. KidMix’s SmartZone provides an entertaining collection of safe, regulated, kid-approved articles and videos. The SmartZone enables kids to learn more about their favorite subjects including: science, history, cooking, sports, music, art, and more. All articles, music and videos have been screened to determine they are suitable for a younger audience. All articles, music and videos can be liked, shared with connected friends, and favorited to your child’s own profile page for future reference. Articles cannot be shared outside of the KidMix Application and there are no external links that could re- direct your child to another website or application.</p>
